# Daemon output — scraping results stay on local disk only, NEVER public repo
# (2026-04-27). bmw_corpus + future scrapers append to JSONL files that
# eventually exceed GitHub's 100MB per-file cap. History rewrite for the
# 11 already-pushed auto-commits is tracked separately as a force-push task.
output/
*.jsonl
*.jsonl.processed

# Local safety backups from filter-repo / similar rewrites — never tracked
.git.backup-*/
